/>\n<br />\n2.多啲去行下,走下,曬下<br />\n襯行得走得,去多啲地方<br />\n<br />\n3.食清啲,唔好咁多味精,鼓油<br />\n搵下秋葵,蘆筍既食物,有幫助<br />\n<br />\n4.標靶藥岩唔岩食? 如果醫生話適合食標靶藥既話其實會好有效<br />\n<br />\n4期唔代表無得醫,但辛苦就緊嫁喇<br />\n加上去左淋巴度應該有排搞<br />\n但千其唔好灰心<br />\n家人陪同俾到佢好大支持,唔好咁易放棄"},{"pid":"969bccc760179eb2795cf243f2263ecd86b0e58b","tid":999664,"uid":174052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:28:23.000Z","msg":"師兄一定要媽媽保持正面心態 呢樣係好重要 千奇唔好太負面"},{"pid":"661c3c7b42e03ba6ee4205cbca74f470411ff2c9","tid":999664,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"老豆大腸癌三期 遲啲要食藥做化療 過程係咪好辛苦會成個人瘦哂 我有啲咩可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a53f7807f0e993e2abe4f98a2bcbed0851a91edc","tid":999664,"uid":161126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:33:12.000Z","msg":"以我所知 有營養奶飲既"},{"pid":"75d98509debbe32fa689254df1312031064cdf6e","tid":999664,"uid":1210,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:35:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0bc5013eb5f74ed7477b66ee91e0e20191fa402f","tid":999664,"uid":2482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"661c3c7b42e03ba6ee4205cbca74f470411ff2c9","tid":999664,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"老豆大腸癌三期 遲啲要食藥做化療 過程係咪好辛苦會成個人瘦哂 我有啲咩可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:59:55.000Z","msg":"陪伴"},{"pid":"77013ec289fef0d409d5759627a304e5e5b628e6","tid":999664,"uid":78039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:03:40.000Z","msg":"無方法，要比d精神力量佢"},{"pid":"f4b94fd768b838125c9bbce2a6fe2d3a36270e2c","tid":999664,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:05:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"01e9dfe1d61a2eaabecda0f6f82930c15e05a784","tid":999664,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29