e9","tid":999664,"uid":43309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:25:29.000Z","msg":"加油我！！！實冇事嫁"},{"pid":"b61b2cef23c65c63f43fc70b7b2d00b7c17cacba","tid":999664,"uid":63452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59c3955b808c78a21a3da7e8830024d88c15b7b8","tid":999664,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:06:58.000Z","msg":"食姬松茸 或靈芝 可以減輕化療前後不適"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T04:28:43.000Z","msg":"有無咩證據support?"},{"pid":"bf80b0bd95782228e9c36c5f35dc94ff21e0478b","tid":999664,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:02:49.000Z","msg":"早幾年嚴浩介紹布緯食療，唔知有無效<br />\n雖然不能依賴，但如果無副作用得閒試下好過無"},{"pid":"3eae05815826f1a43270c91c37a2d4282505e709","tid":999664,"uid":77580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8cb13b35ec3d4a424cb7bd946fc1ed40097f6fad","tid":999664,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14768798b7886b0a512bb743584bc698375b79e2","tid":999664,"uid":77580,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"661c3c7b42e03ba6ee4205cbca74f470411ff2c9","tid":999664,"uid":58630,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:31:16.000Z","msg":"老豆大腸癌三期 遲啲要食藥做化療 過程係咪好辛苦會成個人瘦哂 我有啲咩可以做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"我米八做果時得返48kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T03:48:33.000Z","msg":"你原本幾重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T05:10:33.000Z","msg":"我第4期先發現,癌細胞可能一早已經侵蝕緊我,所以一路都低過60kg,而家冇事先肥返d"},{"pid":"8bb5e8b3289c7be0f54a7abb5b80aaacde2ceb33","tid":999664,"uid":59870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T06:47:48.000Z","msg":"樓主想知道更多資訊可以tg我 我係NPC康復者~<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/vincent2541\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fvincent2541&d=AMPtd42ADahZ7WU%2BVKQ9tTPUa9iY%2BpOmOVTB4fMSqaQ%3D&h=695c3b80\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/vincent2541</a>"},{"pid":"17de44c3cd259123a9522b4e3d95cbd312cab8ad","tid":999664,"uid":176985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得食oral impact好似幾好<br />\n我爸爸都係鼻咽癌第三期，同步電療化療七星期，一開頭已經剝左好多大牙，得一對大牙用到<br />\n加上打完順鉑無晒胃口，到week 2已經換晒每日飲4包oral impact(即飲個隻，見人話沖粉難飲d)，中途發燒入過一次院，但最後做得晒所有電療化療<br />\n同期做電療既病人到一半d頸已經損晒流晒水，我爸叫做keep到下體重(電療既治療師話太瘦就電唔中，我地焗我爸飲夠4包，之前一直話難飲唔肯飲4包)，條頸都係一塊手指尾指甲咁上下大細損左，所以覺得包野係有d料到<br />\n不過真係貴，計返一個月都成五千蚊一個月，阿爸阿媽一開始都接受唔到要全程飲奶，但後來經過醫生姑娘營養師言語治療師勸都係接受左<br />\n樓主支持住啊，當初我都頂住頭家，扮強勢指揮做d咩，夜晚就自己一個人喊<br />\n有咩需要問可以pm"},{"pid":"d48441d84c52c7b213c52e0d31473c2c0fa406b4","tid":999664,"uid":59526,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6e886a28364a7903bbc633125c9ebd3a88a9175","tid":999664,"uid":82710,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-29T02:15:44.000Z","msg":"飲湯，唔洗名貴野，<br />\n越攰越要行兩步，手持羅漢果水去下海旁散步chill<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n皮膚乾燥搽cream當係飲水咁密就OK<br />\n千其唔好禁食，各式保健品如與藥物無衝突可以食(安慰劑效果居多)<br />\n曾患癌化療現職護狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:51:40.000Z","msg":"絲打係咪KCC?"},{"pid":"206ccd676d7cf9fb85f8a21fa58576b1ddce4b2d","tid":999664,"uid":1654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"其實應該做埋高壓氧增強效果，<br />\n唔知點解香港唔興"},{"pid":"e9d347f13cf7ea4e9e853d62dec761e6fe669bae","tid":999664,"uid":42986,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:10:34.000Z","msg":"巴打加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"113901894328a67e9817a7b01956b6ce0805966e","tid":999664,"uid":176985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17de44c3cd259123a9522b4e3d95cbd312cab8ad","tid":999664,"uid":176985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T11:47:33.000Z","msg":"我個人覺得食oral impact好似幾好<br />\n我爸爸都係鼻咽癌第三期，同步電療化療七星期，一